Updated workflow graph nodes to better surface connections: taller nodes and multiline in/out connection previews with overflow counts so each node clearly shows linked nodes. Added tests for new connection preview text behavior and updated preview-limit expectation.

Validation: `swift build` passes. `swift test` / `swift test --filter WorkflowGraphConnectionsDisplayTests` fail in this environment due existing `no such module 'XCTest'` errors (baseline issue starting at `AddTaskProjectPreselectionTests.swift`).